{"tid":2343081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥到訪飛行服務隊 讚揚政府飛行服務隊專業 表現卓越","createTime":"2020-12-27T15:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T18:07:38.000Z","uid":291865,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3256cdca42dd376a776411a5c3482a041765c126","tid":2343081,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/a680e27b184ced092fdff6a0c6cb0a26/2020/12/c461388e83a9cc7bdf43e4d07432654f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2Fa680e27b184ced092fdff6a0c6cb0a26%2F2020%2F12%2Fc461388e83a9cc7bdf43e4d07432654f.jpg&h=a1687532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥到訪飛行服務隊並坐直升機視察多個發展項目<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥到訪飛行服務隊總部，讚揚飛行服務隊專業、勇敢，同時向總監胡偉雄了解由香港乘坐直升機，到粵港澳大灣區不同城市的飛行路程和所需時間。她早前在施政報告中表示，國家民航局已同意粵港可開展跨境商用直升機服務的籌備工作，以強化大灣區國際化營商環境。 林鄭月娥之後乘坐直升機，視察多項施政報告提出的發展計劃，包括俯瞰機場三跑填海工程、東涌填海工程、屯門西土地規劃、龍鼓灘、邊境口岸發展，特別是皇崗/落馬洲和羅湖管制站、北環線沿線等。她說，隨著香港融入國家發展大局，加強與深圳合作，會充分考慮如何善用邊境地區或跨境基建附近地點的地理優勢，以把握大灣區機遇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372388/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E5%88%B0%E8%A8%AA%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E9%9A%8A%E4%B8%A6%E5%9D%90%E7%9B%B4%E5%8D%87%E6%A9%9F%E8%A6%96%E5%AF%9F%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E9%A0%85%E7%9B%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2372388%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E9%259A%258A%25E4%25B8%25A6%25E5%259D%2590%25E7%259B%25B4%25E5%258D%2587%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2580%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E9%25A0%2585%25E7%259B%25AE&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjdw8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=8c1f5078\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372388/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E5%88%B0%E8%A8%AA%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E9%9A%8A%E4%B8%A6%E5%9D%90%E7%9B%B4%E5%8D%87%E6%A9%9F%E8%A6%96%E5%AF%9F%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E9%A0%85%E7%9B%AE</a>"},{"pid":"f9010f49b705937df8164760a47c49bd8be14e9a","tid":2343081,"uid":20291,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"呢條仆街小家種到"},{"pid":"a1f4e600753a20570913b4c180d01b81718c1866","tid":2343081,"uid":41458,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:42:55.000Z","msg":"飛狗有冇一隻敢為良知而辭職? <br />\n仲話抗爭, 笑話嚟, 特別係公墓猿. 份工緊要過佢條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c23be67cb4536a0a42eac6483674e9652804fb","tid":2343081,"uid":201512,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T16:12:43.000Z","msg":"飛曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ada1225e0583d7e5706840ae66955973dfefa3a","tid":2343081,"uid":51183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T16:14:33.000Z","msg":"就快用國產零件<br />\n唔成班逃亡就假<br />\n咪出來穩定一下軍心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fce7e8650a966b98985829c1e94bd5d20a514d0","tid":2343081,"uid":199456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T16:21:36.000Z","msg":"講自己做飛行服務隊 就快比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35cd69657ffdf39438bdeca32a9777d7bbb42e7e","tid":2343081,"uid":363330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T16:27:21.000Z","msg":"港共認證<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重視邊度代表邊度就係邪惡爪牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d0bfa24157719ceacaaa468d34d840d81fa3e7","tid":2343081,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T16:56:26.000Z","msg":"祝福邊個死邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s